    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Emmerling Post Changes Its Name</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Bill Carter</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Carter, Bill</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Emmerling Post Advertising in New York is changing its name to Post &amp; Partners to reflect that Peter Post has bought John Emmerling's stake in company; Post, president at Emmerling Post, is named to new post of chief executive at Post &amp; Partners (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Emmerling Post Advertising in New York is changing its name to Post &amp; Partners to reflect that Peter Post has bought John Emmerling's stake in the company. Mr. Post, 53, president at Emmerling Post, was named to the new post of chief executive at Post &amp; Partners. Mr. Emmerling, 62, chief creative officer at Emmerling Post, relinquishes his creative duties to Steve Crane, 43, acting creative director at Emmerling Post, who was named creative director at Post &amp; Partners. Mr. Emmerling continues with the agency as chairman until year's end, and will consult for two years.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Emmerling Post Advertising in New York is changing its name to Post &amp; Partners to reflect that Peter Post has bought John Emmerling's stake in the company. Mr. Post, 53, president at Emmerling Post, was named to the new post of chief executive at Post &amp; Partners. Mr. Emmerling, 62, chief creative officer at Emmerling Post, relinquishes his creative duties to Steve Crane, 43, acting creative director at Emmerling Post, who was named creative director at Post &amp; Partners. Mr. Emmerling continues with the agency as chairman until year's end, and will consult for two years.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
